trans-unit.source: Represents the configuration section for authentication modules.
trans-unit.target: Representerar konfigurationsavsnittet för moduler för autentisering.
Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModulesSection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModulesSection"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: This constructor adds the <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection> class to the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement.Properties%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Lägger till den här konstruktorn i <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection>undergrupp till den <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement.Properties%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement.Properties%2A> </xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of authentication modules in the section.

The <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection> returned by this property contains one <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElement> for each authentication module in the configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection>returneras av den här egenskapen innehåller en <xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElement>för varje autentiseringsmodul i konfigurationsfilen.</xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElement> </xref:System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection"></xref> that contains the registered authentication modules.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Net.Configuration.AuthenticationModuleElementCollection"> </xref> som innehåller autentiseringsmodulerna som registrerade.
